    <item>
      <title>南非将于年底前公布新金融规则提案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/south-africa-to-publish-proposed-new-financial-rules-by-year-end</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非国家财政部表示，其即将完成期待已久的国家金融市场监管改革，并计划在今年年底前公布拟议的修正案以供评论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/south-africa-to-publish-proposed-new-financial-rules-by-year-end</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 08:36:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈克：沙特欢迎油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-01/haque-saudi-would-welcome-higher-oil-prices-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿联酋国民银行首席经济学家兼研究主管 Khatija Haque 表示，沙特阿拉伯欢迎油价上涨。她补充说，由于中国需求疲软，她预计 OPEC+ 不会放松减产。Khatija Haque 还在 Horizo​​ns Middle East and Africa 上与 Joumanna Bercetche 讨论了沙特阿拉伯的经济前景。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-01/haque-saudi-would-welcome-higher-oil-prices-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 07:24:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>飞机停飞导致 Wizz Air 利润下滑，股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/wizz-air-shares-sink-as-aircraft-groundings-cut-into-profit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受夏季旅游旺季飞机停飞的影响，廉价航空公司 Wizz Air Holdings Plc 下调了今年的利润预期，股价出现疫情初期以来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/wizz-air-shares-sink-as-aircraft-groundings-cut-into-profit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 07:20:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国兴业银行汽车业务业绩不佳导致欧洲股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/european-stocks-edge-lower-after-glum-results-from-autos-socgen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汽车行业和法国兴业银行的一系列业绩令人失望，欧洲股市因此下跌。这让美联储可能在下个月降息的迹象黯然失色。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/european-stocks-edge-lower-after-glum-results-from-autos-socgen</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 07:14:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波尔：中东仍未爆发全面战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-01/bohl-still-short-of-all-out-war-in-the-middle-east-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[RANE 高级 MENA 分析师 Ryan Bohl 表示，尽管《纽约时报》报道称伊朗已下令对以色列进行报复性打击，但我们仍未爆发全面战争。他还在 Horizo​​ns Middle East and Africa 上与 Joumanna Bercetche 讨论了真主党的回应及其对停火谈判的影响。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-01/bohl-still-short-of-all-out-war-in-the-middle-east-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 05:58:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Chanana：预计美元短期内将走弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-01/chanana-expect-dollar-to-weaken-in-short-term-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[盛宝外汇策略主管 Charu Chanana 表示，美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔的鸽派言论为 9 月降息敞开了大门，但问题是美联储能降息到什么程度。她补充说，她预计美元今年将受到美联储和美国大选的影响而走弱。Charu Chanana 还在 Horizo​​ns Middle East and Africa 上与 Joumanna Bercetche 讨论了日元和英镑。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-01/chanana-expect-dollar-to-weaken-in-short-term-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 05:55:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
